title: Pink Floyd - Monopoly [bootleg]
description:
The Wall part is recorded at Nassau Coliseum, N.Y. on 28th of February, 1980.
Sadly, Bring The Boys Back Home is missing, but the CD's instead include the three last songs, recorded live in the Birmingham Town Hall on 11th of February, 1970.
Sysyphus was only played live three or sotimes but someone was able to record this one.
The violence sequence is a collection of several parts which was played a couple of times in the eary 1970, it include parts that would later be included in Money and Us & Them.
